feMorphology\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feOffset\"><code>&lt;feOffset&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/fePointLight\"><code>&lt;fePointLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpotLight\"><code>&lt;feSpotLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTile\"><code>&lt;feTile&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feTurbulence\"><code>&lt;feTurbulence&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font\"><code>&lt;font&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face\"><code>&lt;font-face&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-format\"><code>&lt;font-face-format&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-name\"><code>&lt;font-face-name&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-src\"><code>&lt;font-face-src&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/font-face-uri\"><code>&lt;font-face-uri&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>G\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/g\"><code>&lt;g&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyph\"><code>&lt;glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>H\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/hkern\"><code>&lt;hkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>I\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>J-L\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/linearGradient\"><code>&lt;linearGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>M\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/metadata\"><code>&lt;metadata&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section><p></p>\n\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong><code>pathLength</code></strong>&nbsp;attribute lets authors specify a total length for the path,&nbsp;in user units. This value is then used to calibrate the browser's distance calculations with those of the author, by scaling all distance computations using the ratio&nbsp;<code>pathLength</code>/(<em>computed value of path length</em>).</p>\n\n<p>This can affect the actual rendered lengths of paths; including text paths, animation paths, and various stroke operations. Basically, all computations that require the length of the path. <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-dasharray\">stroke-dasharray</a></code>, for example, will assume the start of the path&nbsp;being&nbsp;0 and the end point&nbsp;the value&nbsp;defined in the&nbsp;<code>pathLength</code>&nbsp;attribute.</p>\n\n<p>Seven elements are using this attribute: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/circle\"><code>&lt;circle&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/ellipse\"><code>&lt;ellipse&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a>, and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"topexample\">\n\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 100 60<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n  <span class=\"token selector\">path</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">fill</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">stroke</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> black<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">stroke-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">stroke-dasharray</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- No pathLength, the real length of the path is used. In that case, 100 user units --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M 0,10 h100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- compute everything like if the path length was 90 user units long --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M 0,20 h100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">pathLength</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>90<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- compute everything like if the path length was 50 user units long --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M 0,30 h100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">pathLength</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- compute everything like if the path length was 30 user units long --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M 0,40 h100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">pathLength</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>30<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- compute everything like if the path length was 10 user units long --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M 0,50 h100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">pathLength</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"topExample sample\" id=\"frame_topexample\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/pathLength/_sample_.topexample.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"circle","title":"circle","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/circle\"><code>&lt;circle&gt;</code></a>, <code>pathLength</code> lets authors specify a total length for the circle,&nbsp;in user units.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><em>none</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ellipse","title":"ellipse","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/ellipse\"><code>&lt;ellipse&gt;</code></a>, <code>pathLength</code> lets authors specify a total length for the ellipse,&nbsp;in user units.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><em>none</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"line","title":"line","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/line\"><code>&lt;line&gt;</code></a>, <code>pathLength</code> lets authors specify a total length for the line,&nbsp;in user units.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><em>none</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"path","title":"path","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a>, <code>pathLength</code> lets authors specify a total length for the path,&nbsp;in user units.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><em>none</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polygon","title":"polygon","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a>, <code>pathLength</code> lets authors specify a total length for the shape,&nbsp;in user units.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><em>none</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyline","title":"polyline","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code></a>, <code>pathLength</code> lets authors specify a total length for the shape,&nbsp;in user units.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><em>none</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rect","title":"rect","isH3":false,"content":"<p>For <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/circle\"><code>&lt;circle&gt;</code></a>, <code>pathLength</code> lets authors specify a total length for the rectangle,&nbsp;in user units.</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a></strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Default value</th>\n   <td><em>none</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Specification","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/paths.html#PathLengthAttribute\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 2<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">pathLength</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/paths.html#PathLengthAttribute\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">pathLength</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"circle","id":"circle"},{"text":"ellipse","id":"ellipse"},{"text":"line","id":"line"},{"text":"path","id":"path"},{"text":"polygon","id":"polygon"},{"text":"polyline","id":"polyline"},{"text":"rect","id":"rect"},{"text":"Specification","id":"specification"}],"summary":"The pathLength attribute lets authors specify a total length for the path, in user units. This value is then used to calibrate the browser's distance calculations with those of the author, by scaling all distance computations using the ratio pathLength/(computed value of path length).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"pathLength","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/pathlength","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/pathlength/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/pathLength","title":"pathLength"}],"pageTitle":"pathLength - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}